"{\"uid\": \"jamaicaobserver.com-2024-02-08-shelly-ann-fraser-pryce-retire-paris-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"MIAMI,\\u00a0United States\\u00a0(AFP)- Jamaican sprint legend Shelly-Ann Fraser-Pryce, a three-time Olympic gold medalist and 10-time world champion, said she will retire after this year's Paris Olympics in an interview published Thursday.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 228, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 28, \"end\": 36, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\", \"score\": 0.999999968224302, \"rank\": 3.177565647555872e-08, \"text\": \"Jamaican\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\"}, {\"begin\": 51, \"end\": 74, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shelly-Ann_Fraser-Pryce\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Shelly-Ann Fraser-Pryce\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shelly-Ann_Fraser-Pryce\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shelly-Ann_Fraser-Pryce\"}, {\"begin\": 178, \"end\": 192, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking to the American magazine Essence, Fraser-Pryce said she is forcing herself to retire at age 37 to spend more time with her family.\", \"from\": 230, \"to\": 369, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 246, \"end\": 254, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9990201436982802, \"rank\": 0.0009790761603980054, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 264, \"end\": 271, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Essence\", \"score\": 0.9999999969591045, \"rank\": 2.6641386902822237e-09, \"text\": \"Essence\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Essence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Essence\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My son needs me,\\\" Fraser-Pryce told the magazine.\", \"from\": 371, \"to\": 421, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My husband and I have been together since before I won in 2008.\", \"from\": 422, \"to\": 486, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He has sacrificed for me.\", \"from\": 487, \"to\": 512, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are a partnership, a team.\", \"from\": 513, \"to\": 542, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's because of that support that I am able to do the things that I have been doing for all these years.\", \"from\": 544, \"to\": 649, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And I think I now owe it to them to do something else.\\\"\", \"from\": 650, \"to\": 705, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She is focusing on her training for one last chance at Olympic glory in France, what Fraser-Pryce said is about \\\"pushing boundaries\\\" as well as \\\"showing people that you stop when you decide.\", \"from\": 707, \"to\": 897, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 779, \"end\": 785, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.8443873310394531, \"rank\": 0.15360799461011385, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I want to finish on my own terms.\\\"\", \"from\": 899, \"to\": 934, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Fraser-Pryce has won eight Olympic medals, including 100-metre gold at 2008 in Beijing and 2012 in London and a Tokyo Olympic title as part of Jamaica's 4\\u00d7100 relay.\", \"from\": 936, \"to\": 1101, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1015, \"end\": 1022, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.99999999888405, \"rank\": 1.1159450730560976e-09, \"text\": \"Beijing\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1035, \"end\": 1041, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.999990245866962, \"rank\": 8.130880212084472e-06, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}, {\"begin\": 1048, \"end\": 1053, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9830263895073972, \"rank\": 0.017266684587279195, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1079, \"end\": 1086, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.9999998903258589, \"rank\": 8.682590058817188e-08, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her medal haul also includes silver at 100m in Tokyo and 200m in London plus a 2016 Rio 100m bronze.\", \"from\": 1103, \"to\": 1203, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1150, \"end\": 1155, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9830263895073972, \"rank\": 0.017266684587279195, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1168, \"end\": 1174, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.999990245866962, \"rank\": 8.130880212084472e-06, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She won 100m world titles in 2009, 2013, 2015, 2019 and 2022 plus a 200 world crown in 2013 and 4\\u00d7100 relay golds in 2009, 2013, 2015 and 2019.\", \"from\": 1205, \"to\": 1348, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is not a day I am getting up to go practice and I am like, 'I am over this,'\\\"\\u00a0Fraser-Pryce said.\", \"from\": 1350, \"to\": 1453, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"HOUSE RULES\", \"from\": 1457, \"to\": 1468, \"entities\": []}]}"